3. Background-repeat:

 <style>
            body { background-image:url(image/pic4.gif); background-repeat: repeat;}
        </style>


4. Background-position:

 <style>
            body { background-image:url(image/pic4.gif); background-position: 200px 200px;}
        </style>

5. Background-attachment:

 <style>
            body { background-image:url(image/pic4.gif); background-attachment:local; }
        </style>

6. Background:

 <style>
            body { background: #ffffff url(image/pic4.gif) repeat fixed; }
        </style>

Just change the style below:

